<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>彭博加密货币</title><link>https://bloomberg.com/crypto/</link><description>彭博加密货币</description><lastBuildDate>Fri, 06 Mar 2026 12:29:55 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>随着交易员评估伊朗的波动性，比特币小幅下跌</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-06/bitcoin-btc-edges-downward-as-traders-take-stock-of-iran-volatility</link><description>周五，由于投资者对中东事态发展仍感到紧张，比特币在 70,000 美元大关附近窄幅波动。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/igIKnsTrADrc/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 06 Mar 2026 11:53:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-06/bitcoin-btc-edges-downward-as-traders-take-stock-of-iran-volatility</guid></item><item><title>美国证券交易委员会 (SEC) 结束针对加密货币亿万富翁贾斯汀·孙 (Justin Sun) 的诉讼</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-05/sec-ends-case-against-crypto-billionaire-justin-sun</link><description>美国证券交易委员会表示，随着监管机构继续解决拜登政府期间提起的大量数字资产执法案件，它将结束对加密货币亿万富翁孙宇晨及其附属公司的诉讼，并将支付 1000 万美元。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iq5PO.foQG2M/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 05 Mar 2026 21:59:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-05/sec-ends-case-against-crypto-billionaire-justin-sun</guid></item><item><title>纽约证券交易所所有者以 250 亿美元估值投资加密货币公司</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-05/nyse-owner-invests-in-crypto-exchange-at-25-billion-valuation</link><description>InterContinental Exchange Inc. 在一笔交易中收购了 OKX 的股份，该交易对这家加密货币交易运营商的估值为 250 亿美元。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iX9U6LVeDTsY/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 05 Mar 2026 12:56:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-05/nyse-owner-invests-in-crypto-exchange-at-25-billion-valuation</guid></item><item><title>SEC 杠杆 ETF 在即将到来的加密货币洪水面前冻结</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2026-03-05/the-sec-s-leveraged-etf-freeze-ahead-of-the-looming-crypto-flood</link><description>在特朗普政府采取更加宽松的监管态度的背景下，美国证券交易委员会对日益激进的基金结构提出了担忧。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/i.6x4qVOHFlE/v8/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 05 Mar 2026 22:00:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2026-03-05/the-sec-s-leveraged-etf-freeze-ahead-of-the-looming-crypto-flood</guid></item><item><title>由于伊朗动荡笼罩市场，比特币的涨势动摇</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-05/bitcoin-btc-holds-firm-above-70-000-as-global-assets-recover</link><description>比特币正在努力维持上涨势头，而全球市场在伊朗持续冲突造成数日波动后仍面临压力。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/ig2GanXlEmLA/v2/1200x-1.png" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 05 Mar 2026 02:10:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-05/bitcoin-btc-holds-firm-above-70-000-as-global-assets-recover</guid></item><item><title>加密货币公司 Zerohash 申请国家信托银行执照</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-04/crypto-firm-zerohash-applies-for-national-trust-bank-charter</link><description>数字资产公司 Zero Hash US LLC 向美国货币监理署提交了一份国家信托银行执照申请。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iuxwMq_Y8oPg/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 04 Mar 2026 20:51:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-04/crypto-firm-zerohash-applies-for-national-trust-bank-charter</guid></item><item><title>人工智能的繁荣刺激了比特币销售，对持有 80 亿美元的矿商构成了威胁</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-04/ai-boom-spurs-bitcoin-sales-threat-at-miners-holding-8-billion</link><description>多年来，最大的比特币矿商在经营时都遵循着一种信念和商业模式：他们铸造的比特币值得持有，稀缺性会奖励耐心，数字货币的资产负债表积累本身就是一种竞争护城河。他们中的一些人建立了价值数亿美元的藏品。他们称之为财政战略。公牛队称之为信念。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iyYdy0sIE6xI/v3/1200x-1.png" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 04 Mar 2026 20:44:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-04/ai-boom-spurs-bitcoin-sales-threat-at-miners-holding-8-billion</guid></item><item><title>Kraken 是第一家确保美联储支付访问权限的加密货币公司</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-04/crypto-exchange-kraken-secures-fed-payment-access</link><description>Kraken 已获得堪萨斯城联邦储备银行授予的有限用途账户，使其成为第一家直接访问美国央行支付基础设施的数字资产银行。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/i1.bNVXDduTE/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 04 Mar 2026 12:48:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-04/crypto-exchange-kraken-secures-fed-payment-access</guid></item><item><title>Tradeweb 通过押注外汇风格市场推动加密货币发展</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-04/tradeweb-makes-crypto-push-with-bet-on-fx-style-market-structure</link><description>机构资金开始从加密货币交易所转移到看起来更像华尔街的场外交易场所。 Tradeweb Markets Inc. 领投了 3100 万美元，认为这种转变才刚刚开始。&lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="http://assets.bwbx.io/images/iP8D8NG6dNzI/v2/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 04 Mar 2026 13:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-04/tradeweb-makes-crypto-push-with-bet-on-fx-style-market-structure</guid></item><item><title>伊朗 78 亿美元的加密货币市场在战争中引起新的关注</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-04/iran-s-7-8-billion-crypto-market-draws-fresh-attention-in-war</link><description>美国-以色列对伊朗的战争让该国 78 亿美元的加密货币市场重新受到关注，该国公民和当局在动荡时期越来越多地转向该市场存储和汇款。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/ilsFYJFUvElw/v3/1200x-1.png" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 04 Mar 2026 13:00:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-04/iran-s-7-8-billion-crypto-market-draws-fresh-attention-in-war</guid></item></channel></rss>